title: Annuar to face Mara audit committee tomorrow
text:
More 
Suspended Mara chairperson Annuar Musa has been summoned to face the federal agency’s internal audit committee at its meeting to be held tomorrow. 
Mara interim chairperson Yusof Yacob today said that Annuar has been called to ensure justice in ongoing probe into graft allegations linked to sponsorship of The Red Warriors, Kelantan’s official football team.
